snippet.title: Midnight Ultra: Devil's Path Update
snippet.description:
http://store.steampowered.com/app/731590/Midnight_Ultra/

It's finally here! The Devil's Path update adds a big pack of new and improved content to Midnight Ultra for FREE, including:

-2 new weapons
-6 new enemies
-3 new maps
-A brand-new, two-part boss battle
-6 new songs
-10+ new themes
-Reworked audio for all weapons
-Reworked melee attacks
-Mac and Linux support
-Mouse inversion, sensitivity, and audio options

Follow us at http://forwardinstinct.com/
